# Track only markdown files in this repo.
# Ignore everything by default, then re-allow:
#   - the root .gitignore
#   - any directory (so git descends to find .md files inside)
#   - any .md file at any depth
# Note: gitignore does not support inline comments, so each rule is on its own line.

*
!/.gitignore
!*/
!*.md
